column3: *Due to missing sex data, the total number of cases reported by sex may not correspond with the total number of cases reported for a disease.
Seasonal year from September to August (eg. 2018/19 includes cases from September 1, 2018 to August 31, 2019).
As of May 1 2018, malaria and yellow fever were removed from the reportable disease list for Ontario.
Excludes infectious, late latent and congenital syphilis.
